ut he did feel a secret joy: now this would put an end to school. They pleaded with him during the course of a week.

His mother, of course, cried. His father threatened to take away his new chess set — enormous pieces on a morocco board. And suddenly —

everything was decided of itself. He ran away from home — in his autumn coat, since his winter one had been hidden after one unsuccessful attempt to run away — and not knowing where to go (a stinging snow was falling and settling on the 